import React, {Component} from 'react';
import { Button, Form, Grid, Header, Image, Message, Segment, Input, GridColumn } from 'semantic-ui-react';
import Layout from '../../components/layout.js'
import { Link } from '../../routes';
import post from '../../localmodules/express_post';


class RegisterForm extends Component {

    state = {
        address : {
            pin :'',
            house:'',
            area:'',
            district:'',
            state:'',
        },
        name : {
            firstName : '',
            middleName : '',
            lastName : ''
        },
        email : '',
        aadhar : '',
        res : ''
    };

    onSubmit = (event) => {
        event.preventDefault();
    }


    render() {
        console.log(this.state.res);
        return (
            <Layout>
                <Grid verticalAlign='middle' >
                    <Grid.Column width={2}></Grid.Column>
                    <Grid.Column width={12}>
                        <Header as='h2' color='blue' textAlign='center' style={{margin : '35px 35px'}}>
                            {this.state.res}
                        </Header>
                        <Form onSubmit={this.onSubmit}>
                            <Form.Group widths='equal'>
                                <Form.Field>
                                    <label>First Name</label>
                                    <Input
                                        placeholder = 'First Name'
                                        value={this.state.name.firstName}
                                        onChange={event => this.setState({ name: { firstName: event.target.value }})}
                                    />
                                </Form.Field>
                                <Form.Field>
                                    <label>Middle Name</label>
                                    <Input
                                        placeholder = 'Middle Name'
                                        value={this.state.name.middleName}
                                        onChange={event => this.setState({name : { middleName: event.target.value }})}
                                    />
                                </Form.Field>
                                <Form.Field>
                                    <label>Last Name</label>
                                    <Input
                                        placeholder = 'Last Name'
                                        value={this.state.name.lastName}
                                        onChange={event => this.setState({ name : { lastName: event.target.value }})}
                                    />
                                </Form.Field>
                            </Form.Group>
                            <Form.Group>
                                <Form.Field width={8}>
                                    <label>House</label>
                                    <Input
                                        placeholder = 'House'
                                        value={this.state.address.house}
                                        onChange={event => this.setState({ address : { house : event.target.value }})}
                                    />
                                </Form.Field>
                                <Form.Field width={8}>
                                    <label>Area</label>
                                    <Input
                                        placeholder = 'Area'
                                        value={this.state.address.area}
                                        onChange={event => this.setState({ address : { area : event.target.value }})}
                                    />
                                </Form.Field>
                                
                            </Form.Group>

                            <Form.Group>
                                <Form.Field width={6}>
                                    <label>District</label>
                                    <Input
                                        placeholder = 'District'
                                        value={this.state.address.district}
                                        onChange={event => this.setState({ address : { district : event.target.value }})}
                                    />
                                </Form.Field>
                                <Form.Field width={6}>
                                    <label>State</label>
                                    <Input
                                        placeholder = 'State'
                                        value={this.state.address.state}
                                        onChange={event => this.setState({ address : { state : event.target.value }})}
                                    />
                                </Form.Field>
                                <Form.Field width={4}>
                                    <label>Pin</label>
                                    <Input
                                        placeholder = 'Pin'
                                        value={this.state.address.pin}
                                        onChange={event => this.setState({ address : { pin : event.target.value }})}
                                    />
                                </Form.Field>
                            </Form.Group>

                            <Form.Group>
                                <Form.Field width={8}>
                                    <label>House</label>
                                    <Input
                                        placeholder = 'House'
                                        value={this.state.address.house}
                                        onChange={event => this.setState({ address : { house : event.target.value }})}
                                    />
                                </Form.Field>
                                <Form.Field width={8}>
                                    <label>Area</label>
                                    <Input
                                        placeholder = 'Area'
                                        value={this.state.address.area}
                                        onChange={event => this.setState({ address : { area : event.target.value }})}
                                    />
                                </Form.Field>
                                
                            </Form.Group>

                            <Form.Group widths='equal'>
                                <Form.Field >
                                    <label>Email</label>
                                    <Input
                                        placeholder = 'Email'
                                        type = 'email'
                                        value={this.state.address.email}
                                        onChange={event => this.setState({ email : event.target.value })}
                                    />
                                </Form.Field>
                                <Form.Field>
                                    <label>Aadhar</label>
                                    <Input
                                        placeholder = 'Aadhar'
                                        value={this.state.address.aadhar}
                                        onChange={event => this.setState({ aadhar : event.target.value })}
                                    />
                                </Form.Field>
                            </Form.Group>
                            <Form.Group widths='equal'>
                                <Form.Field >
                                    <label>Password</label>
                                    <Input
                                        placeholder = 'Password'
                                        type = 'password'
                                        value={this.state.address.password}
                                        onChange={event => this.setState({ password : event.target.value })}
                                    />
                                </Form.Field>
                                <Form.Field>
                                    <label>Confirm Password</label>
                                    <Input
                                        placeholder = 'Confirm Password'
                                        type = 'password'
                                        value={this.state.address.confirmPassword}
                                        onChange={event => this.setState({ confirmPassword : event.target.value })}
                                    />
                                </Form.Field>
                            </Form.Group>
                            <Button primary>Submit</Button>
                            
                        </Form>
                    </Grid.Column>
                    <Grid.Column width={2}></Grid.Column>
                </Grid>
            </Layout>
        );
    }
}

export default RegisterForm;
